Добавление ролей:

CREATE USER 'rl_admin'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'solarwinds123';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON `schema_atvechau`.* TO 'rl_admin'@'localhost';
CREATE USER 'rl_customer'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'solarwinds123';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON `schema_atvechau`.* TO 'rl_customer'@'localhost';
CREATE USER 'rl_leader_group'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'solarwinds123';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON `schema_atvechau`.* TO 'rl_leader_group'@'localhost';
CREATE USER 'rl_employee_groupe'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'solarwinds123';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON `schema_atvechau`.* TO 'rl_employee_groupe'@'localhost';
CREATE USER 'rl_accountant'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'solarwinds123';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON `schema_atvechau`.* TO 'rl_accountant'@'localhost';
CREATE USER 'rl_scheduler'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'solarwinds123';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON `schema_atvechau`.* TO 'rl_schedulern'@'localhost';

Проверка прав ролей:

SHOW GRANTS FOR 'rl_admin'@'localhost';
SHOW GRANTS FOR 'rl_customer'@'localhost';
SHOW GRANTS FOR 'rl_leader_group'@'localhost';
SHOW GRANTS FOR 'rl_employee_groupe'@'localhost';
SHOW GRANTS FOR 'rl_accountant'@'localhost';
SHOW GRANTS FOR 'rl_scheduler'@'localhost';
